text: Podcast: 'Triple Option' previews prep football playoffs Podcast: 'Triple Option' previews prep football playoffs Iowa Prep Sports , Iowa Prep Sports , Iowa Prep Sports Podcast , Prep Football , Photos West Delaware's Sam Maloney tries to break a tackle by Independence's Luke House (center) during the first quarter of their WaMaC Conference high school football game at West Delaware High School in Manchester, Iowa, on Friday, Oct. 16, 2015. The Hawks and Mustangs are each top-10 ranked teams heading into the Class 3A playoffs. (Jim Slosiarek/The Gazette) Most Popular
